<abstract><t>This document presents a topology-transparent zone in an OSPF area. A topology-transparent zone comprises a group of routers and a number of links connecting these routers.  Any router outside of the zone is not aware of the zone.  The information about the links and routers such as a link down inside the zone is not advertised to any router outside of the zone.</t></abstract>

